{
  "stem": "2718.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because one or two of the-- of the managers, there were engineers-- we suspected, and we'll never know for sure-- has volunteered to take on the-- the task to run the factory and not to have-- you know, without-- without-- without the owners.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they-- the result was that the whole family was taken out and put into the-- put-- taken-- taken out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was already in June.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until June, we-- we managed to-- we were one of the last ones to arrive into the-- into the brick factory, which was on the [? siding-- ?] railway [? siding ?] where we eventually got loaded into the-- into the cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "June, '44?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was June, '44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- we-- we didn't stay very long there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, eventually, we had to, and I-- I remember the time when we were marched.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] must have been hundreds of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were among the hundreds of people who came last.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were marched through the whole of the town from the ghetto-- from the ghetto to the-- to the brick factory, which was a long, long, long march, a very long march.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I would say, easily, 10 kilometers-- more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that march, everybody could take one suitcase-- one suitcase with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember my grandfather marching, or walking, with a-- with a stick, and a-- and a [? pack ?] on the stick, because he couldn't carry a-- a suitcase.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was one-- one of the last-- one of the last memories of him as I-- as I remember it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And but what I also remember, the crowd which was lining the streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
